<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Just a funny <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/30747147.267413/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY29pbmRlc2suY29tL2J=
1c2luZXNzLzIwMjMvMDMvMDQvbXVsdGljb2luLWNhcGl0YWxzLWhlZGdlLWZ1bmQtbG9zdC05MT=
QtbGFzdC15ZWFyLWludmVzdG9yLWxldHRlci1yZXZlYWxzLw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0=
94032d6" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" s=
tyle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wid=
th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;"> series of numbers here</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Multicoin Capital=E2=80=99s hedge fund lost 91=
.4% in 2022, according to a copy of the firm=E2=80=99s annual investor lett=
er viewed by CoinDesk.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The letter attributed last year=E2=80=99s decl=
ine to a turbulent year for cryptocurrencies, as well as direct and indirec=
t impact from the collapse of crypto exchange FTX.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CWhile the fund successfully dodged th=
e catastrophic implosions of LUNA and Three Arrows Capital earlier in the y=
ear, we didn=E2=80=99t avoid the explosive revelations about FTX nor the su=
bsequent contagion that spread across the market,=E2=80=9D said the letter.=
 =E2=80=9CAfter a remarkable year in 2021, our performance in 2022 was the =
worst since inception.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Despite the massive drawdown, Multicoin=E2=80=
=99s hedge fund remains up 1,376% net of fees from its inception through 20=
22. As the broader crypto market rebounded from last year=E2=80=99s lows, M=
ulticoin reported that the fund gained 100.9% in January 2023, bringing the=
 fund=E2=80=99s inception-to-January return to 2,866%.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You will sometimes hear traders talk about the=
 importance of avoiding drawdowns in terms of simple arithmetic: =E2=80=9CI=
f you=E2=80=99re down 50% one year, you have to be up 100% the next year to=
 make up for it,=E2=80=9D that sort of thing. In those terms it is very=C2=
=A0bad to be down 90% for the year, because even if you=E2=80=99re up 100% =
the next year you=E2=80=99re still down 80% from your high. But Multicoin=
=C2=A0<em>was=C2=A0</em>up 100% in the first=C2=A0<em>month=C2=A0</em>of 20=
23, after being down 91% in 2022. And if you were in the fund from the begi=
nning, you have still made a lot of money, because I guess they=E2=80=99ve =
had more up-100% months than down-90% months. You probably weren=E2=80=99t =
in the fund from the beginning =E2=80=94=C2=A0probably the up-100% months a=
ttracted investors =E2=80=94=C2=A0but never mind. =E2=80=9CMulticoin says i=
t =E2=80=98remains steadfast=E2=80=99=C2=A0in its long term strategy and =
=E2=80=98does not attempt to time the market.=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D</p>
